sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Event
    participant W as Workflow
    participant J as Judge
    participant R as Runtime
    participant T as Tool
    participant P as Policy
    participant A as Audit

    E->>W: trigger
    W->>J: verify
    J-->>W: pass
    W->>R: execute
    R->>T: call tool
    T->>P: check policy
    P-->>T: allow or deny
    T-->>R: result
    R->>A: record execution
